{
  "name": "einvoice-void-with-approval — Slack approval gate → svc/v1/void",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## einvoice-void-with-approval (entry) — v0.28.0 hardened\n\n**v0.28.0 fixes (from V&V findings)**\n- `$resumeUrl` is NOT a real n8n variable. Corrected to `$execution.resumeUrl`.\n- State (correlationId / provider / input / requestedBy / reason) is restamped AFTER Wait via `$node['Stamp correlation'].json` (Wait drops upstream state by default).\n- Webhook responseMode = `responseNode` (fixed JSON schema, no internal leak).\n- HTTP node uses `fullResponse: true` so audit row's `status` checks real statusCode.\n- Asia/Taipei timezone set.\n- SEC-9 carryover: approver identity STILL comes from the resume webhook caller (n8n public-API limit); for production put HMAC verifier (e.g. Slack `X-Slack-Signature`) in front of the resume URL — see SECURITY-REVIEW.md.\n\n**Why void needs a human gate**: void is irreversible. Approver owns the audit trail.\n\n**Trigger**: webhook POST `/webhook/einvoice/void`.\n```json\n{ \"provider\": \"amego\", \"requestedBy\": \"jane@company.tw\", \"reason\": \"客戶取消訂單\", \"input\": { \"invoiceNumber\": \"AB12345678\", \"reason\": \"客戶取消\" } }\n```\n\n**Before activating**: replace `__REPLACE_ME__EINVOICE_SVC_URL__`, `__REPLACE_ME__SLACK_CHANNEL__`, `__REPLACE_ME__GOOGLE_SHEET_ID__`.\n\n---\n\n## 中文 — einvoice-void-with-approval（入口 / 作廢人工核可）\n\n**為何需要人工核可**：作廢不可逆。按 approve 的人對 audit 負責。建構在 `examples/templates/human-approval-gate.workflow.json` 之上。\n\n**觸發**：CS / 管理 UI 打 `POST /webhook/einvoice/void`。\n\n**Body**：見上方 JSON 範例。\n\n**流程**：\n1. 蓋 correlationId、發 Slack 訊息含 `$execution.resumeUrl/approve` 和 `$execution.resumeUrl/reject`。\n2. Wait 最多 4 小時。\n3. 收到 approve → 打 svc/v1/void → 寫 audit row。\n4. 收到 reject 或 timeout → 只寫 audit row、不打 svc。\n\n**🔒 上線前硬化**：\n- Wait 節點接受任何 POST 到 `$execution.resumeUrl/approve` — 上線版前面必須加 reverse proxy 或 inbound Webhook + HMAC-SHA256 驗簽（`X-Slack-Signature` 或你 IdP 等價物）。詳見 `skills/tigerai/n8n-security-governance` §6。\n- audit row 的 `approver` 欄位**不可信任 caller 自報**，必須來自 Slack 驗簽過的 user 識別。\n\n**上線前需替換**：`__REPLACE_ME__EINVOICE_SVC_URL__`、`__REPLACE_ME__SLACK_CHANNEL__`（**不要 #general，請用 #einvoice-ops 等可審查 channel**）、`__REPLACE_ME__GOOGLE_SHEET_ID__`",
        "height": 900,
        "width": 580
      },
      "id": "note-1",
      "name": "Pattern note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -740,
        -400
      ]
    },
